
Function: CLRSCRN

Syntax:   (CLRSCRN)

Returns:

 NIL, after clearing the screen of a 3270-type terminal.

Processing:

 TCAM/VTAM conventions are adhered to in order to insure, whenever
 possible, that line messages are not lost when the screen is cleared.

Errors signaled:

 None.

Notes:

Examples:

 (CLRSCRN)     ... returns NIL after clearing the screen.

